  "description": "<i>Gaiflame</i> (or <i>Gai Flame</i>) is sci-fi, turn-based strategy, with giant, heavy armed humanoid robots. The player controls an army of giant robots and try to destroy enemies.<br><br>The game starts with macro-level view of the world (player can move units from battlefield to battlefield - each battlefield has 6 slot for troops), and battle mode - player commands several robots on a &quot;fake-hexes&quot; based map (squares with 6 neighbors) and tries to defeat the enemy's army. Fight between robots are animated on special, small screen - like in <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Advance+War\">Advance War</a>.",
